PENCULIKAN AYAKA TASHIRO

205
00:16:00,876 --> 00:16:01,752
Ohyama.

206
00:16:03,921 --> 00:16:04,922
Jadi,

207
00:16:05,798 --> 00:16:06,674
tentang...

208
00:16:07,716 --> 00:16:10,386
yang kukatakan kemarin...

209
00:16:16,600 --> 00:16:18,936
