385
00:36:16,090 --> 00:36:17,925
Apa-apaan ini?

386
00:36:18,301 --> 00:36:21,596
Dia kurus, tingginya sekitar 165 cm,
mungkin terbiasa memakai pisau bedah.

387
00:36:21,679 --> 00:36:23,764
Dia membunuh Hashimoto,
